To create a "requirements.txt" file:
    pip freeze > requirements.txt

To automatically install pip dependencies from "requirements.txt" file:
    pip install -r requirements.txt

Launch Jupyter Notebooks
    jupyter notebook

Launch Jupyter Lab (newer)
    jupyter lab
    jupyter lab --no-browser

To run Jupyter Lab in 'app mode'
    Mac OS:
        Chrome --app=file:///C:/Users/Alex/AppData/Roaming/jupyter/runtime/jpserver-21276-open.html
    Windows Desktop:
        cd "C:\Program Files (x86)\Google\Chrome\Application\"
        .\chrome.exe --app= <url from startup>

To quit (shutdown) Jupyter
    Ctrl+C